@startuml staleness_window
!include ../theme.iuml

title Staleness window: kdy uživatel vidí starý read model

actor User as u
participant "Controller" as ctrl
participant "Command Bus" as cb
participant "Order Aggregate" as agg
database "Write DB" as wdb
queue "Event Bus" as eb
participant "Projector" as p
database "Read Model" as rm

== T0: User odešle command ==

u -> ctrl : POST /orders\n{items, address}
ctrl -> cb : PlaceOrder cmd
cb -> agg : place(items, address)
agg -> wdb : INSERT order, INSERT outbox
agg -> eb : OrderPlaced event
ctrl --> u : 201 Created\n{ orderId: 42 }
note right of u : T+0 ms: command potvrzen

== T0–T100ms: STALENESS WINDOW ==

note over u, rm
  Zde je read model starý:
  GET /orders/42 vrátí 404, protože projector
  ještě eventu nezpracoval.
end note

u -> ctrl : GET /orders/42
ctrl -> rm : SELECT * WHERE id=42
rm --> ctrl : NULL ⚠️
ctrl --> u : 404 Not Found 😕

== T+100ms: projector dohnal stav ==

eb -> p : OrderPlaced event
p -> rm : INSERT INTO orders_view\n(id=42, ...)

== T+150ms: read model konzistentní ==

u -> ctrl : GET /orders/42 (retry)
ctrl -> rm : SELECT * WHERE id=42
rm --> ctrl : data
ctrl --> u : 200 OK ✓

note over u
  UI vzory pro řešení staleness:
  1. Optimistic update (UI ukáže ihned, mark "pending")
  2. Wait-and-poll (klient čeká 100–500 ms, pak GET)
  3. Read your writes (sync GET z primary, ne z read modelu)
end note

@enduml
